channel.title: Total noob question
channel.description: When the server runs it launches a control panel interface separately from the command prompt of the server. In that interface there are commands you may execute. I tried to look for them in sever.java, commands.java, player.java, and client.java but no luck. When I put a command in commands.java it won't give me an error when compiling, but when I try and use the command in-game, it doesn't work :(, help please?
